## Implementation Plan: `@ai-sdk/pixelart` Provider Package

### Overview

This plan adds a new fictional "PixelArt" AI provider to the Vercel AI SDK that supports **only image generation**. The package follows the exact structure and conventions of `@ai-sdk/luma`, simplified because PixelArt uses a synchronous API (POST returns base64 images directly, no polling required).

---

### Step 1: Create `packages/pixelart/package.json`

